### Example 07 - Remote Router (proxy.Router)
### Mock Weather API: http://localhost:9001
### Main App: http://localhost:3001

# ========================================
# Mock Weather API (Direct Access)
# ========================================

### Get current weather - Jakarta
GET http://localhost:9001/weather/jakarta

### Get current weather - Bandung
GET http://localhost:9001/weather/bandung

### Get forecast - Jakarta (5 days)
GET http://localhost:9001/forecast/jakarta?days=5

### Get forecast - Surabaya (3 days)
GET http://localhost:9001/forecast/surabaya?days=3

# ========================================
# Main App - Weather Reports
# ========================================

### Create weather report - Jakarta with forecast
POST http://localhost:3001/weather-reports?city=jakarta&forecast=true&days=5

### Create weather report - Bandung (current only)
POST http://localhost:3001/weather-reports?city=bandung&forecast=false

### Create weather report - Surabaya with 3-day forecast
POST http://localhost:3001/weather-reports?city=surabaya&forecast=true&days=3

### Create weather report - Invalid city (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3001/weather-reports?city=tokyo&forecast=false
